    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras/828aa4aaf58ed8a6074691a86720bb10.avif?t=1757868982\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras_big/828aa4aaf58ed8a6074691a86720bb10.avif?t=1757868982 width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras/5e12b725019ee6e09355a76ddda5b549.poster.avif?t=1757868982\" width=720 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras/5e12b725019ee6e09355a76ddda5b549.webm?t=1757868982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras/5e12b725019ee6e09355a76ddda5b549.mp4?t=1757868982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the frontier lands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture through dusty desert bluffs, snow-capped mountains, and the shadowy ruins of ancient cult hideouts. Battle ruthless outlaws in campaign missions, high-stakes elimination contracts, and relentless wave-based survival challenges. But the outlaws aren’t the only danger—a mysterious cult faction lurks beneath the surface. Unlock new weapons through use in combat, and customize your experience with four selectable difficulty levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras/be8497cedd4562251caffb5769da5f30.poster.avif?t=1757868982\" width=720 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras/be8497cedd4562251caffb5769da5f30.webm?t=1757868982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras/be8497cedd4562251caffb5769da5f30.mp4?t=1757868982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the weaponry that suits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you prefer the accuracy of a rifle, the close-range power of a shotgun, or the speed of sidearms, your weapons shape how you fight. Each class has multiple variants to suit different approaches. From the solid hit of a crossbow to the sheer volume of a Gatling gun, you'll have plenty of hot lead dispensers to choose from. You can even dual-wield sidearms if you want to trade precision for raw firepower.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras/e3b7361dc4603e6ba6d1911609026f55.poster.avif?t=1757868982\" width=720 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras/e3b7361dc4603e6ba6d1911609026f55.webm?t=1757868982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227060/extras/e3b7361dc4603e6ba6d1911609026f55.mp4?t=1757868982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The outlaws' bullets are fast, but you’re faster. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use bullet time to line up your shots. Sprint and dash to stay mobile, keeping pressure where it hurts. Swap weapons on the fly to always have the right tool for the job. During a reload, mashing the reload key speeds it up, and every second counts when you’re under fire. You’re equipped for the fight. The rest is up to you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current Game Content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Main Missions, about 1:00 - 1:30 hours in total</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 Side Missions, each about 5 minutes long</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 Weapons: 7 Rifles, 4 Shotguns, 5 Sidearms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Difficulties</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >19 Achievements</p></li></ul>",
